msgstr "YITH WooCommerce Featured Audio and Video Content Premium"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-featured-audio-video-"
"content/"
msgstr ""
"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-featured-audio-video-"
"content/"

#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"<code><strong>YITH WooCommerce Featured Audio and Video Content</strong></"
"code> allows you to set a video or audio instead of the featured image on "
"the single product page. Also, you can add video or audio to a different "
"gallery under the featured content. <a href=\"https://yithemes.com\">Get "
"more plugins for your e-commerce shop on <strong>YITH</strong></a>."
msgstr ""
"<code><strong>YITH WooCommerce Featured Audio and Video Content</strong></"
"code> ti permette di impostare un video o audio al posto dell'immagine in "
"evidenza sulla pagina prodotto. Inoltre puoi anche aggiungere audio e video "
"ad una galleria diversa sotto il contenuto in evidenza. <a href=\"https://"
"yithemes.com\">Ottieni più plugin per il tuo e-commerce su <strong>YITH</"
"strong></a>."

#. Author of the plugin/theme
msgid "YITH"
msgstr "YITH"

